name: Hot Latina (Face LoRA)
description:
Join my new Discord here! https://discord.gg/cnVvnkgtPb

Hot Latina (aka MixedLatina) - a LoRA trained on AI-generated images only, this LoRA is meant to give your female models a more tropical/Latina look to them. Enjoy :P

Recommended Settings

  • For txt2img: LoRA weight of 0.1-0.6

  • For img2img: LoRA weight of 0.1-0.6

  • Steps: >=10 (minimum), >=20 (for some models)

  • Best models: LazyMix+, URPM, qgo10b, LofiSasha, Liberty Main

    • RealisticVision, Deliberate, others are good too, but may need to lower LoRA weight or increase # of steps

  • Mix this LoRA with other prompt words or LoRAs (i.e. pale, american, asian) to get a sexy mixed look

Background

I saw a girl on TikTok yesterday that made me want to do this. Latina girls are incredibly sexy and I didn't see any on here.

This LoRA went through 4 trials. Initial versions had an undesired tendency to make the background always brown. I updated the training images to have more variety to resolve this, but there still might be a slight brown bias with this LoRA at higher weight values (>0.5) when the background isn't specified in the prompt.

Prompt in Model Comparison

photo of a latina woman, skinny, MixedLatina, wearing bra, (((symmetrical))), (studio background, professional, portrait photo, blurred white background), smile, laughing, (highly detailed skin), realistic skin texture, ((full body)), looking at viewer, facing front, closeup, colorful, 4k, <lora:MixedLatina LORA:0.4>
Negative prompt: (nude:1.6), detailed background, deformed face, tattoo, watermark, ((deformed)), paintings, sketches, ((black and white)), (worst quality:2), (low quality:2), (normal quality:2), lowres, normal quality, ((monochrome)), ((grayscale)), skin spots, acnes, skin blemishes, age spot, glans

Steps: 20, Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras, CFG scale: 7, Seed: 4237493148, Size: 440x600

Contact me at aihotgirls@proton.me
